<div><div id='zzq8iv3c0g361stRiverDetailGadget2' class='CRiverDetailGadget-detail CRiverDetailGadget'><div class='controls'><h1>Big Panther Creek - Old Hwy 441 to dirt road off Yonah Lake Road</h1>
<div><div id='zzq8iv3c0g361stArticleGadget26Container' class='CArticleGadget-view CArticleGadget'><div id='zzq8iv3c0g361stArticleGadget26-1' class='contents'></div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
